'''Krzysztof Martens''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Awards===

* [[Mott-Smith Trophy]] (1) 2008

===Wins===

* [[World Transnational Open Teams Championship]] (1) 1997 <ref>[http://www.worldbridge.org/transnational-open-teams.aspx World Transational Open Teams Winners]</ref>

* [[World Team Olympiad|World Olympiad Teams Championship]] (1) 1984

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (1)
